{"data":[{"id":561609260,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"294f2cca7ad735b07edf8ff480bf103d","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561609260","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545982741,"updated_time":1545982741,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你还是要老老实实高考，老老实实千军万马过独木桥，你追不上的妹子还是追不上，语文课上背不出课文还是会被罚抄。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e请问如果回答是这样，题主还会发自内心地想要证明哥德巴赫猜想么？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560496570,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"10595a1a65d91082327a72e619bcdb2b","url_token":"zhang433832","name":"zhang433832","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/10595a1a65d91082327a72e619bcdb2b","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560496570","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545842974,"updated_time":1545843051,"extras":"","is_copyable"